Parfait 👍 Voici la version en anglais, prête à poser dans ta slide avec 3 blocs/personas :

⸻

Le Comptoir: a tool for everyone

👩‍💻 End-user (employee)
	•	Arrives at the counter with a need (incident, onboarding, information…)
	•	Registers at the welcome tablet
	•	Is quickly assisted and directed to the right coach

🧑‍🔧 Coach / Technician
	•	Receives requests in real time
	•	Follows a guided workflow (waiting, handling, resolution, closure)
	•	Uses simplified tools (signature, traceability, automated forms)

👨‍💼 Manager / Team Lead
	•	Accesses Power BI dashboards to monitor activity
	•	Relies on accurate KPIs (waiting, processing, satisfaction)
	•	Can steer, compare counters, and identify improvements

⸻

